<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Welcome to <%= name %>'s Portfolio</h1>
    <img class="profile_pic" src="/images/profile Small.png" alt="profile_pic">
    <h2>About Me</h2>
        <p> I am a software developer student passionate about creating beautiful and fun things. I am studying at BYU-Idaho in Rexburg Idaho and can't wait to learn more! I want to learn more about Web Development and Game frameworks in the future. I love learning new things and improving myself. </p>

        <h3>Languages Skills</h3>
        <div class="list-container">
            <ul class="skills">
                <li>HTML</li>
                <li>CSS</li>
                <li>Python</li>
                <li>C#</li>
                <li>Javascript</li>
                <li>Erlang</li>
                <li>Rust</li>
            </ul>

        <h3>Interests</h4>
            <ul class="interests">
                <li>web development</li>
                <li>computer systems</li>
                <li>game frameworks</li>
                <li>classical & romantic piano</li>
                <li>oil & acrylic painting</li>
                <li>embroidery</li>
                <li>clay work</li>
                
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        

    <a href="/projects">View My Projects</a>

    <h2>Contact Me</h2>
    <form id="contact-form">
        <input type="text" id="name" placeholder="Your Name" required>
        <input type="email" id="email" placeholder="Your Email" required>
        <textarea id="message" placeholder="Your Message" required></textarea>
        <button type="submit">Send Message</button>
    </form>
    <p id="confirmation-message"></p>

    <script src="/js/scripts.js"></script>

</body>
</html>
